Module: home
Description: Simple home page with API hello endpoint

========================================
1. App.java - Add imports
========================================

Open: src/main/java/dev/jms/app/App.java
Add at the top:

import dev.jms.app.home.handler.HelloHandler;

========================================
2. App.java - Register routes
========================================

Add in PathTemplateHandler section:

paths.add("/api/home/hello", route(new HelloHandler(), ds));

========================================
3. config.js - Add module configuration
========================================

Open: vite/src/config.js
Add in MODULE_CONFIG:

home: {
  path: '/home',
  container: 'main',
  authorization: null,
  persistent: false,
  priority: 999,
  init: null
}
